import { Box, Container, Paper, Grid, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

function DynamicForm() {
  return (
    <Container>
    <Paper component={Box} p={4} mx="auto">
    <Grid container  spacing={3}>
        <Grid item md={3}>
           <TextField  
            label="Name"
            placeholder="Enter your full name"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={3}>
           <TextField  
            label="Emai"
            placeholder="Enter your Email address"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={3}>
           <TextField  
            label="Phone"
            placeholder="Enter your phone number"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={3}>
           <TextField  
            label="Address"
            placeholder="Enter your full address"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
    </Paper>
       </Container>

  )
}

export default DynamicForm
